\"text-on-surface-variant text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10 md:mb-12\">Looking for a specific color, size, or a unique gift idea? I specialize in bringing your imagination to life through the rhythmic dance of the hook and yarn.</p><div class=\"space-y-6 md:space-y-8 mb-10 md:mb-12\"><div class=\"flex gap-4 md:gap-6 items-start\"><span class=\"w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 rounded-full bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-container flex items-center justify-center font-bold shrink-0 text-sm md:text-base\">1</span><div><h4 class=\"font-bold text-base md:text-lg\">Vision</h4><p class=\"text-sm md:text-base text-on-surface-variant\">Share your inspiration or sketches with me on WhatsApp.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-4 md:gap-6 items-start\"><span class=\"w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 rounded-full bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-container flex items-center justify-center font-bold shrink-0 text-sm md:text-base\">2</span><div><h4 class=\"font-bold text-base md:text-lg\">Details</h4><p class=\"text-sm md:text-base text-on-surface-variant\">We&#x27;ll select the perfect fibers, colors, and textures together.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-4 md:gap-6 items-start\"><span class=\"w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 rounded-full bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-container flex items-center justify-center font-bold shrink-0 text-sm md:text-base\">3</span><div><h4 class=\"font-bold text-base md:text-lg\">Magic</h4><p class=\"text-sm md:text-base text-on-surface-variant\">I meticulously hand-stitch your piece with care and intention.</p></div></div></div><a class=\"min-h-[48px] inline-flex justify-center w-full sm:w-auto items-center gap-3 px-6 md:px-8 py-4 rounded-full bg-primary text-white font-semibold hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity text-sm md:text-base text-center\" href=\"/custom-order\">Start Your Custom Order Form ✍️</a></div><div class=\"relative\"><div class=\"aspect-square rounded-full overflow-hidden border-[12px] border-surface-container relati